## üìö API Reference

### Main Classes

| Class | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `LAGC` | Main simulator interface |
| `StabilizerGraph` | Graph state management |
| `TensorSlicer` | Memory-efficient contraction |
| `LossRecovery` | Error mitigation |
| `HardwareModel` | Noise modeling |
| `TopologyGenerator` | Lattice creation |

```python
from lagc import (
    LAGC,
    StabilizerGraph,
    TensorSlicer,
    LossRecovery,
    HardwareModel,
    TopologyGenerator,
)
```

